{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/en/blog/2016-05-11-donation","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"After a break of 9 months of pregnancy laziness, I resumed ‘flow’ donation (every 2 months). I don’t know what I’m\ndoing this for? It is not…","fields":{"langKey":"en","slug":"/en/blog/2016-05-11-donation/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"May 11, 2016","title":"Donation"},"html":"<p>After a break of 9 months of <del>pregnancy</del> laziness, I resumed ‘flow’ donation (every 2 months). I don’t know what I’m\ndoing this for? It is not paid, I don’t give a shit to help someone, It is not rewarded with enough food, it hurts, the\nHonorary Donor is not honorable at all. The tangible advantages are a free blood test for various diseases and a free\nday off from work on the day of blood donation + an additional day off. Intangible – training the body to produce blood.\nHere’s the process:</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 3120px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/69985cc151628d4a132405b9bf77f3f7/1fc44/ruka.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/69985cc151628d4a132405b9bf77f3f7/f696c/ruka.avif 1920w,\n/static/69985cc151628d4a132405b9bf77f3f7/0bce3/ruka.avif 3120w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 3120px) 100vw, 3120px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/69985cc151628d4a132405b9bf77f3f7/882b9/ruka.webp 1920w,\n/static/69985cc151628d4a132405b9bf77f3f7/c4c01/ruka.webp 3120w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 3120px) 100vw, 3120px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/69985cc151628d4a132405b9bf77f3f7/0f98f/ruka.jpg 1920w,\n/static/69985cc151628d4a132405b9bf77f3f7/1fc44/ruka.jpg 3120w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 3120px) 100vw, 3120px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/69985cc151628d4a132405b9bf77f3f7/1fc44/ruka.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Hand\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Hand</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Blood is taken twice: for a preliminary analysis (with a thin needle) and, in fact, the blood donation itself is already\nfrom the other hand (pictured). Today they gave me a SURPRISE: while peeling off the plaster that holds the needle in\nthe vein, the nurse jerked the needle very rudely, somehow at an angle. I was almost pissed, how disgusting and painful\nin a new way. And here’s the result:</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 4160px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/a3429/paket.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/f696c/paket.avif 1920w,\n/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/a5563/paket.avif 3840w,\n/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/8d91f/paket.avif 4160w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 4160px) 100vw, 4160px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/882b9/paket.webp 1920w,\n/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/93e07/paket.webp 3840w,\n/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/39c10/paket.webp 4160w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 4160px) 100vw, 4160px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/0f98f/paket.jpg 1920w,\n/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/e6b01/paket.jpg 3840w,\n/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/a3429/paket.jpg 4160w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 4160px) 100vw, 4160px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/da34b6ba3c624eaa92a14f2ea6443df1/a3429/paket.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Package\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Package</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Yes, too little. You can’t pay bills with donation “salary” (hello, “Senseless”). P. S. I’m not a loader, I’m a\nphotoblogger.</p>","id":"997955bd-eb6b-5f43-a1e0-9eceed0a16cc"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ITFarrier"}}},"pageContext":{"langKey":"en","language":"en","next":{"fields":{"langKey":"en","slug":"/en/blog/2016-05-28-bard-ring/"},"frontmatter":{"language":null,"title":"Bard‐ring","type":"post"}},"previous":{"fields":{"langKey":"en","slug":"/en/blog/2016-04-25-mayakovsky-readings/"},"frontmatter":{"language":null,"title":"Mayakovsky Readings","type":"post"}},"slug":"/en/blog/2016-05-11-donation/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2674376943","357539041","4035578580"],"slicesMap":{}}